For structured deposits, the documents required to be presented at Alfa Bank by individuals (foreign citizens or stateless persons) include:
- Passport or another identity document recognized in Russia;
- Notarized translation of the document into Russian;
- Certificate of registration with the tax authority (if available).

For stateless persons residing permanently in Russia:
- Residence permit.

For other stateless persons:
- Document issued by a foreign state recognized as an identity document;
- Temporary residence permit or residence permit.
